4G/LTE Module
-------------

|Product| is equipped with a **mini-PCIe connector** that can connect to a 4G/LTE module.
The customer will also need a SIM Card Holder and a 4G/LTE Antenna Connector to ensure 4G/LTE works on the |product|. SIM card does NOT support hot plug. Power off before inserting or removing SIM card.

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A72/Others/4G_module.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *mini-PCIe Connector & 4G Module*

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A72/Others/4G_com.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *SIM Card Holder & 4G Antenna*

